panels.name: Sent Bandwidth
panels.queryString:
$$SonicWall
| parse "sent=* " as sent_bytes
| parse "rcvd=* " as rcvd_bytes
| sum(sent_bytes) as sent_bytes
| sent_bytes / 1024 / 1024 as sent_mbytes
| fields -sent_bytes

panels.name: Top 10 Messages
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*sonicwall*
| if(isBlank(msg), "none", msg) as msg
| count msg
| sort _count
| limit 10

panels.name: Top 10 Source IPs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*sonicwall*
| where !isBlank(src_ip)
| count by src_ip
| sort _count
| limit 10

panels.name: Opened and Closed Connections Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*sonicwall*
| where msg matches "*Closed*" or msg matches "*Opened*"
| if(msg matches "*Opened*", 1, 0) as connection_opened
| if(msg matches "*Closed*", 1, 0) as connection_closed
| timeslice 1m
| sum(connection_opened) as opened, sum(connection_closed) as closed by _timeslice

panels.name: Bandwidth Served Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$SonicWall
| parse "sent=* " as sent_bytes
| parse "rcvd=* " as rcvd_bytes
| timeslice 1m
| sum(rcvd_bytes) as rcvd_bytes, sum(sent_bytes) as sent_bytes by _timeslice
| rcvd_bytes / 1024 / 1024 as rcvd_mbytes
| sent_bytes / 1024 / 1024 as sent_mbytes
| fields -rcvd_bytes, sent_bytes

panels.name: Received Bandwidth
panels.queryString:
$$SonicWall
| parse "sent=* " as sent_bytes
| parse "rcvd=* " as rcvd_bytes
| timeslice 1m
| sum(rcvd_bytes) as rcvd_bytes
| rcvd_bytes / 1024 / 1024 as rcvd_mbytes
| fields -rcvd_bytes

panels.name: Threat Table
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_ip_address _sourcecategory=*sonicwall*
| 0 as malicious_score
| if(malicious_confidence matches "high", 3, malicious_score) as malicious_score
| if(malicious_confidence matches "low", 2, malicious_score) as malicious_score
| sum(_count) as threats, avg(malicious_score) as malicious_score by ip_address, malicious_confidence, Actor,_source, _sourceCategory
| sort malicious_score, threats, ip_address
| fields -malicious_score

panels.name: Activity by Protocol
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*sonicwall*
| parse "proto=*/" as proto
| count by proto

panels.name: Threats Over Time
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_ip_address
| timeslice 1h
| sum(_count) as threats by _timeslice, malicious_confidence
| transpose row _timeslice column malicious_confidence

panels.name: Outbound Destinations
panels.queryString:
$$SonicWall
| where !compareCIDRPrefix("172.16.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("192.168.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(16)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("10.0.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(8)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.17.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.18.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.19.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.20.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.21.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.22.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.23.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.24.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.25.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.26.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.27.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.28.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.29.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.30.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12)) and !compareCIDRPrefix("172.31.0.0", dst_ip, toInt(12))
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = dst_ip
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code
